I had misread a post from someone who had already spent 31 skill points (I'd love to know where he *got* 31 skill points already...) and I had read it as confirmation of my original assumption that each stage of a skill costs the same number of points.<br>
<br>
But upon close examination, I see that you're right, for the Arch. skills for example, it's actually a 2/4/6 progression in cost. So your table is correct, and I apologize for misunderstanding the actual point costs per stage and presuming that you had misunderstood them instead.<br>
